@startuml
title Sequence Diagram - Dang xuat
autonumber
autoactivate on

actor "Nguoi dung" as User
participant "Frontend" as FE
participant "API Gateway" as GW
participant "Identity Service" as IDS

User -> FE: Chon dang xuat
FE -> GW: Gui yeu cau dang xuat
GW -> IDS: Chuyen tiep yeu cau
IDS -> IDS: Kiem tra phien dang nhap

alt Phien con hieu luc
  IDS -> IDS: Huy phien dang nhap
  IDS --> GW: Tra ket qua thanh cong
  GW --> FE: Tra ket qua
else Khong co phien hop le
  IDS --> GW: Tra ket qua thanh cong
  GW --> FE: Tra ket qua
end

FE -> FE: Xoa trang thai dang nhap
FE --> User: Chuyen ve man hinh dang nhap

@enduml
